data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your dream home nestled in the picturesque community of Forest Creek. This stunning property offers a perfect blend of modern amenities and serene natural surroundings.    Welcome to your slice of paradise in Forest Creek, where modern comfort meets the tranquility of nature. Nestled in this picturesque community, this stunning home boasts 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and approximately 1430 square feet of living space, all set on a charming corner lot enveloped by lush landscaping.    Upon entering, you're greeted by an open-concept floor plan that floods the interior with natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere for both everyday living and entertaining. The spacious kitchen is a focal point, featuring newer appliances and ample counter space, perfect for hosting gatherings with friends and family.    Retreat to the tranquil master suite, complete with a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom, offering a private oasis to unwind after a long day. Additional features include an attached 1-car garage for convenience and ease of access. A/C was replaced in July of 2021. The exterior was repainted in 2022.     Forest Creek offers an array of community amenities, including two sparkling pools for relaxation and entertainment, walking trails, a serene pier and gazebo overlooking the lake, a dog park for furry companions, a basketball court for friendly games, a clubhouse for social gatherings, a fitness room for staying active, and playgrounds plus much more.    Conveniently located in Parrish, FL, this home provides easy access to nearby schools, shopping centers, dining options, and major highways, ensuring that you're never far from the essentials of daily life while enjoying the peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of city living.    Don't let this opportunity slip away – seize the chance to make this your forever home! Schedule your showing today and experience the perfect blend of modern living and serene surroundings in Forest Creek.
